---
title: Unstuffed Pepper Stew with Cheddar Cheese
description: This flavour-packed stew with juicy ground beef, herbs, tender veggies and rice and is the way to go when you don't have the time or inclination to stuff peppers!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/unstuffed-pepper-stew-52ad53f2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/unstuffed-pepper-stew-61f90349e249521ae93c613d-c1a78709.pdf
